  m_text: "Dealer Rules: \nThe dealer must hit until they reach at least 17.\n\nWin:
    \nYour total is higher than the dealer\u2019s, or the dealer busts. You double
    the bet.\n\nLoss: \nThe dealer\u2019s total is higher than yours, or you busted
    first. You loose you bet.\n\nPush: \nIf you and the dealer have the same total,
    it\u2019s a tie and your bet is returned."
