  m_text: "Hit: \nTake another card to get closer to 21. You can hit as many times
    as you like, but if your total exceeds 21, you Bust and lose instantly.\n\nStand:
    \nKeep your current total and end your turn.\n\nBlackjack: \nIf your first two
    cards are an Ace and a 10-value card, you have a \"Natural 21\" and usually win
    automatically."
